00:32:46.470 --> 00:32:51.970
I just want to begin by thanking
Karin and Shaun and Colleen

00:32:51.970 --> 00:32:54.200
and Travis for inviting
me here today.

00:32:54.200 --> 00:32:56.820
It's nice to see some
